request.description:
列出 artifact 上最近 50 条 AI 自动改写事件（note-refine apply）

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** 响应 { artifact_id, rows: [...] }

获取 artifact 的 correction 状态（whole + 各 block）

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** 响应 { artifact_id, whole, blocks }

写入一条 CorrectArtifactEvent（retract/supersede/mark_wrong/restore）

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** correction_kind 枚举：supersede|retract|mark_wrong|restore；supersede 须带 replacement_artifact_id；block_id 可选；reason_md 1..2000；响应 { correction_event_id }

