request.description:
软删除（归档）一条 learning record

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** 无 body，无 version，不经乐观锁；响应 {ok:true}

将 started 的 review session 暂停为 paused

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** 无需 body；sendBeacon 友好；返回 {ok:true,status:'paused'}

将 abandoned 的 review session 重新置为 started

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** 无需 body；返回 {ok:true,status:'started'}

将 paused 的 review session 恢复为 started

**Path vars:** `:id` — set under the request's Path Variables (placeholder `REPLACE_*`).

**Notes:** 无需 body；返回 {ok:true,status:'started'}
